[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare chronic-disease coach decomposes into eleven logical stages: enrollment and care-plan instantiation, longitudinal-store management, biometric-data ingestion, engagement scheduling, channel entry, input safety screening with continuous-emergency-screening, identity-and-context loading, conversation handling with care-plan-grounded responses, output safety screening, escalation routing, and care-team reporting with outcome correlation. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.6 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (longitudinal-memory governance, care-plan-as-code with clinical-leadership ownership, biometric-data integration with clinical thresholds, engagement-policy enforcement with attrition mitigation, and behavior-change-stage tracking with conversation-style adaptation).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CARE-PLAN INSTANTIATION ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolled by care team]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Clinical team identifies patient as appropriate      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for coaching program                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan template selected (per primary chronic     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition; multi-condition variants where the        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institution supports them)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan instantiated with patient-specific values: │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      goals, monitoring frequency, medications, biometric  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      streams, escalation criteria, engagement cadence,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      preferred channels, language preferences             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan signed by clinical team                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient reviews and consents to coaching             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient signs care plan acknowledgment               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed care plan record; coaching enrollment   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    record; longitudinal-store initialization]             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-coach longitudinal store]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care plan reference (id, version)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Behavior-change stage per goal (initialized to       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      best-available estimate from intake)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences (channels, quiet hours,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      topics off-limits, language, name they prefer       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      to be called, names of family members or pets that   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      may surface in conversation)                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Biometric-data baseline                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Adherence-pattern baseline                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Life-context disclosures (initially empty,           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      grows over time)                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outcome-tracking baseline (A1c, BP, weight,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition-specific clinical outcomes)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed on each    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Longitudinal summary: refreshed periodically         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (weekly or per-conversation depending on volume)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coaching]         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── BIOMETRIC-DATA INGESTION ──────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Connected device data sources]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Continuous glucose monitor (CGM) data streams        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Blood pressure cuff readings                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Connected scale weight readings                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Peak flow meter readings (asthma)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pulse oximeter readings (COPD, post-discharge)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Smartwatch data (heart rate, activity, sleep,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      AFib detection where supported)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-reported readings (manual glucose meter,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      manual BP cuff, manual weight)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-reported symptoms via in-app forms or        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Data ingestion pipeline]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-API integration with each device platform     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-self-report integration via app              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Data validation and outlier detection                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Time-series storage with patient-id partitioning     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Threshold evaluation]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-specified thresholds per data type         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Single-reading thresholds (immediate action)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trend thresholds (sustained pattern action)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pattern thresholds (specific patterns of concern)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Event generation]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Threshold-crossing events to engagement scheduler    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Concerning-trend events to escalation pathway        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Routine-data events for trend monitoring             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: biometric-data store; engagement triggers;     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    escalation triggers]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENGAGEMENT SCHEDULING ─────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scheduled engagement sources]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-driven cadence (daily, weekly, monthly)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-milestone triggers (medication start,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      titration, lab follow-up, post-discharge)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Biometric-data-triggered events                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-stated preferences-driven adjustments        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement-fatigue-mitigation policy                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Engagement-policy enforcement]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Maximum daily engagement count (default 1, can be    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      higher per care plan and patient preference)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Quiet hours (default 9pm to 8am local time;          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient-overridable)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel preferences (push, SMS, email, in-app)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Topic-level opt-outs                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement-fatigue detection (low response rates,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      explicit opt-out signals, declining response         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      quality)                                             │
