[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      severe bleeding, suicidal intent)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects condition-specific high-acuity patterns      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (HF: rapid weight gain plus increased dyspnea;       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      asthma: severe exacerbation; diabetes: persistent    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      vomiting suggesting DKA; CKD: hyperkalemia symptoms) │
