[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    501[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      could plausibly involve clinical judgment beyond     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    502[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the care plan, did the response defer to the care    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    503[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      team?                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    504[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Behavior-change-stage-appropriate tone               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    505[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Disclaimer language present where required           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    506[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope check                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    507[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    509[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery, replaced with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    a safer template, or regenerated with corrections]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    511[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    512[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
