[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ESCALATION ROUTING ────────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Escalation triggers]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    517[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-specified thresholds crossed               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute-emergency screening triggered                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive-disclosure pattern detected                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicitly requests human contact            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coach confidence below threshold                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope clinical question requiring care team   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting disclosure detected              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Escalation targets]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute emergency: 911 / 988 / institutional crisis    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with stay-on-the-line guidance                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triage routing (recipe 11.6) for new acute           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      symptoms                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team (PCP, specialist, care manager) for        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition-specific clinical concerns                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy team for medication-specific concerns       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Behavioral-health pathway (recipe 11.8) for          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      mental-health concerns                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care navigation for social-determinants concerns     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting pathway for statutory            │
