[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Real-time alerts]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute escalation events (immediate)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-deviation events (within shift)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-preference-change events (within day)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Periodic reports]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Weekly digest per patient (engagement metrics,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adherence trends, biometric trends, key disclosures, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      open follow-up items)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Monthly summary per patient (longitudinal trends,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      goal progress, behavior-change progress, open        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      issues for the next visit)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Quarterly clinical-review packet for patients        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    569[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      whose care plan is due for review                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    570[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    571[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-team feedback loop]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    572[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team marks alerts as actioned                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    573[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care team requests changes to care plan that the     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    574[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coach picks up on next refresh                       │
